title: Huma on the Hill for closed-door Benghazi testimony, ahead of Clinton appearance
text: Clinton confidante Huma Abedin was on Capitol Hill Friday to testify before the congressional Benghazi committee, just days before the former secretary of state faces off with the panel she has called a political attack arm. ...
